{"tid":798778,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟沙田T4路出現咩問題? 究竟有冇必要","createTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T09:35:19.000Z","uid":108894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e0c8713ae5e2ee5019b42a963adb9bf0f74c9be","tid":798778,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"有興趣研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽講係可以令馬鞍山有直接嘅路去青沙城隧<br />\n但最初推出方案時沙田友屌條公路破壞景觀，又解決唔到問題，又有噪音乜乜77<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但根據我中學經常搭車行果條路同近排搭E41/A47X去機場開工所見，埔公沙田段真係好塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算幾年前擴闊多左一條行車線都冇9用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係起好T4路客觀應該係可以分流左馬鞍山/小瀝源＜＞青沙/城隧嘅車<br />\n但偏偏方案被推倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟T4路是咪可以解決埔公問題<br />\n定係有其他辦法令T4其實冇咩必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43eb67865ba068845135e8c898851638d0e9bdc2","tid":798778,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"試下非繁搭 40x/43x 就知咩事"},{"pid":"2a6ec58d77b184e2aab976344398b438175b05ac","tid":798778,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43eb67865ba068845135e8c898851638d0e9bdc2","tid":798778,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"試下非繁搭 40x/43x 就知咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"直接D啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37724aca8174fddf1f2d2471c2e422bb804844d","tid":798778,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"cctvb舊年講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\