assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟T4路是咪可以解決埔公問題<br />\n定係有其他辦法令T4其實冇咩必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"T4只係令宜家城隧夜晚倒塞既車可以散去河東<br />\n但河東啲路都係full load <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你開T4比尖山用只會令馬𩣑山更多人揸車<br />\n運吉處設計8號仔冇一個出口係正常<br />\nEx 荔枝角同美孚冇方便路可以直上3號或8號仔去機場<br />\n尖山一出就落撚左連翔道返工廠區麻9煩<br />\n大圍出口就霸哂城隧一線令到沙田唯一一條唔塞既隧道都塞埋"},{"pid":"8c06ad1288a4a610b38ae0a486025b562ef3e760","tid":798778,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:09:28.000Z","msg":"已經有幾條路去馬鞍山 <br />\n有咩用"},{"pid":"c6fe63d4c10dd67345a857eafe4e2ff0c0ec1e2e","tid":798778,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"大埔公路沙田段擴闊其實開工未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7df3969d561ebe04b78f321062c493cfd6f2fd1","tid":798778,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fe63d4c10dd67345a857eafe4e2ff0c0ec1e2e","tid":798778,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"大埔公路沙田段擴闊其實開工未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"On9城隧同尖山分流個位可以攪到塞番去大學"},{"pid":"4302c960d0942a45707885999081f309047c33fe","tid":798778,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:24:24.000Z","msg":"一開學，朝早馬鞍山出沙田冇一條路係唔塞<br />\n淨係石門迴旋處同大老山條路嚴重可以塞番入馬鞍山"},{"pid":"1500b32c10c770271d20ff3bbb40d534c7f4f521","tid":798778,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7df3969d561ebe04b78f321062c493cfd6f2fd1","tid":798778,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fe63d4c10dd67345a857eafe4e2ff0c0ec1e2e","tid":798778,"uid":